description: Submission of reserved matters in respect of building design, together with details of levels, means of enclosure, construction details of access roads and junctions, bridge access and associated works from Ordnance Road, cycle parking facilities and refuse storage facilities pursuant to conditions 02, 06, 09, 13, 20 and 25 approved under Ref: TP/04/2623 for redevelopment of site involving erection of 93 residential units (comprising 33 houses and 60 apartments in 2, 3 and 4 storey buildings and being Phase 1 of redevelopment of Plots 4 & 5 for erection of a total of 469 residential units), car parking and construction of access road and new bridge serving the site from Ordnance Road.
